    "body": "You need to epxlicitly tell Geth which hostnames it should serve RPC requests on via `--rpcvhosts=my.domain`. By default it only allows \"localhost\". This is to prevent DNS rebind attacks https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/pull/15962.",
